{"tid":1022300,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［回帶］火星發現巨大冰層！覆蓋直徑 80 公里的隕石坑","createTime":"2019-02-15T02:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T00:40:19.000Z","uid":73804,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"395e876bcd11d837cafc41c75fcf33adb3655c10","tid":1022300,"uid":73804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T02:03:42.000Z","msg":"火星是太陽系中最像地球的行星，尺寸、地質和地球相近，有大氣、水的存在，溫度也相對溫和，因此火星被認為是太陽系中最可能有生命的外星球。人類積極探索火星，除了尋找生命，也探究居住火星的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n近日，歐洲的研究團隊 ESA（The European Space Agency）的 Mars Express 探測器在火星上發現巨大的冰層，將隕石坑完全覆蓋，從外太空來看，就像個巨大的冰淇淋桶，在火星的紅色大地上格外搶眼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sbkbWgN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsbkbWgN.png&h=de270331&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n低溫氣體層覆蓋，火星冰層終年不融化<br />\n<br />\n這個覆蓋冰層的隕石坑名為 Korolev ，由俄國的火箭科學家 Sergey Korolev 命名。它位於火星北半球的低地，奧林匹亞丘地（Olympia Undae）的南方。它的直徑 51 英里（約 82 公里），被冰層完全覆蓋，而隕石坑的中心是冰層最深的地方，大約 1.1 英里（約 1.8 公里），比地球最深的湖泊 &ndash; 貝加爾湖還深（約 1.6 公里），含冰量十分可觀。<br />\n<br />\n這冰層是永凍的。雖然火星和地球一樣有四季交替，這些冰要度過長達 6 個月的火星夏季，但這 1.8 公里深的冰層就個大冰箱。 ESA 說道：「當氣體接近冰層，它會被冷卻，因為冷空氣的密度較高，它會覆蓋在冰層之上，變成一道自然的保溫層。」因為氣體是熱的不良導體，所以這層低溫氣體阻擋外面的熱空氣，讓裡面的冰層常保低溫，度過火星夏日。<br />\n<br />\n在火星，水是很稀少的資源，而在火星的兩極，水可以冰的形式保存下來。如果未來人類在火星上生活，這些冰不但是珍貴的水資源，也會是個觀光聖地，或許西元 3000 年的冬季奧運就在火星上舉行呢！<br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://buzzorange.com/techorange/2018/12/22/ice-crater-on-mars/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Ftechorange%2F2018%2F12%2F22%2Fice-crater-on-mars%2F&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPaf0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=4d0ccfaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://buzzorange.com/techorange/2018/12/22/ice-crater-on-mars/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/science/2018/dec/21/mars-express-beams-back-images-of-ice-filled-korolev-crater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fscience%2F2018%2Fdec%2F21%2Fmars-express-beams-back-images-of-ice-filled-korolev-crater&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPaf0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=5ab67d26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/science/2018/dec/21/mars-express-beams-back-images-of-ice-filled-korolev-crater</a>"},{"pid":"6b8a3c20ef4db3a4d1b0053767379fa68453599c","tid":1022300,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T02:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76331709f1f98dfbeceaf1de3c3b2a13b4740ad","tid":1022300,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T02:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa366e5978cc98b0819abd526813b59f45dcc93","tid":1022300,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T02:25:25.000Z","msg":"真實圖定概念圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc67b10f95f555ef692b507da5622351d06a22a","tid":1022300,"uid":50658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T03:00:19.000Z","msg":"真係有人上咗去嘅話唔好話西元 3000 年，3年都挨唔過"},{"pid":"7d767d8b0bc82d6a5530d3dd45f9859db112de30","tid":1022300,"uid":73804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aa366e5978cc98b0819abd526813b59f45dcc93","tid":1022300,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T02:25:25.000Z","msg":"真實圖定概念圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T03:00:48.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"87b9d7880472f158ee1cb848e897d06e1ef768c8","tid":1022300,"uid":73804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T03:05:32.000Z","msg":"其實70年代已經知火星有冰"},{"pid":"46d3e34b66c44b530ffb50480930f1dd11ca4192","tid":1022300,"uid":5463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aa366e5978cc98b0819abd526813b59f45dcc93","tid":1022300,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T02:25:25.000Z","msg":"真實圖定概念圖<img src=\"/assets/